column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/5f479bec525c8dbf12eb431f22577b62b9a9d63d for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu

As mentioned, you cannot change the versions like this without updating the gitian build. 

If you want to do an update, replace the URLs with ones for the existing versions that work. Closing this issue.
You can't just change versions like this... contrib/gitian-descriptors/deps-win32.yml needs to also be updated\n
I have a pull open, which was intended to update dependcies, AFAIK the last thing I asked for were current Gitian-VM setup instructions there, because Gavin wanted more testers for it.\n

zlib 1.2.6 is still available on sourceforge: http://sourceforge.net/projects/libpng/files/zlib/1.2.6/zlib-1.2.6.tar.gz/download\nsame with libpng 1.5.9: http://sourceforge.net/projects/libpng/files/libpng15/older-releases/1.5.9/libpng-1.5.9.tar.gz/download\n
